          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>SEGA Taiwan 卡片遊戲公開新機台在台設置情報，「SEGA迷你夾娃娃機」於8月1日起在台北・新北 5 間全家便利商店限定設置中。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/41970\">SEGA迷你夾娃娃機 於台北・新北 5 間全家便利商店限定設置 </a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">SEGA Taiwan 卡片遊戲公開新機台在台設置情報，「SEGA迷你夾娃娃機」於8月1日起在台北・新北 5 間全家便利商店限定設置中。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02172342/2025augsegataiwanclawmachinetw01.jpg\" alt=\"2025augsegataiwanclawmachinetw01\" class=\"wp-image-42782\" title=\"SEGA迷你夾娃娃機 於台北・新北 5 間全家便利商店限定設置  1\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02172342/2025augsegataiwanclawmachinetw01.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02172342/2025augsegataiwanclawmachinetw01-300x169.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02172342/2025augsegataiwanclawmachinetw01-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">根據公開資訊，「SEGA迷你夾娃娃機」設置的5間全家便利商店分別為三重三安店、北盛店、廣明店、板橋金典店、中和環球店，目前有柯南、吉伊卡哇、初音等類別。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「SEGA迷你夾娃娃機」每次遊玩費用為40元，營業時間為08:00～22:00，更多資訊可上「SEGA Taiwan 卡片遊戲」FB粉絲專頁查詢。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SegaTaiwan.CardGame\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/SegaTaiwan.CardGame\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> 「SEGA Taiwan 卡片遊戲」FB粉絲專頁</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/41970\">SEGA迷你夾娃娃機 於台北・新北 5 間全家便利商店限定設置 </a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "post-id": {
            "_attributes": {
              "xmlns": "com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"
            },
            "_text": "41970"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": {
            "_text": "DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會"
          },
          "link": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42776"
          },
          "dc:creator": {
            "_cdata": "萌朧雪猴"
          },
          "pubDate": {
            "_text": "Fri, 01 Aug 2025 17:31:36 +0000"
          },
          "category": [
            {
              "_cdata": "DLsite"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "FF45"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=42776"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>將參加FF45的DLsite公開首波參展情報，包含兩本新刊與兩本既刊，及舉辦《別當歐尼醬了！(不當哥哥了！)》作者貓豆腐簽名會，並公開簽名會參與辦法。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42776\">DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">將參加FF45的DLsite公開首波參展情報，包含兩本新刊與兩本既刊，及舉辦《別當歐尼醬了！(不當哥哥了！)》作者貓豆腐簽名會，並公開簽名會參與辦法。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010937/ff45dlsitefirstnews01-1024x584.jpg\" alt=\"ff45dlsitefirstnews01\" class=\"wp-image-42777\" title=\"DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會 2\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010937/ff45dlsitefirstnews01-1024x584.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010937/ff45dlsitefirstnews01-300x171.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010937/ff45dlsitefirstnews01-768x438.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010937/ff45dlsitefirstnews01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">本次兩本新刊包含《勇者與公主與母親大人！？》、《鄰居的文音小姐 總集篇》；既刊則有《在鄉下也就只有這點娛樂了》、《大小姐完全敗北》，購買實體書籍皆會附贈電子版下載序號。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"575\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02-575x1024.jpg\" alt=\"ff45dlsitefirstnews02\" class=\"wp-image-42778\" title=\"DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會 3\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02-575x1024.jpg 575w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02-168x300.jpg 168w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02-768x1369.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02-862x1536.jpg 862w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010951/ff45dlsitefirstnews02.jpg 673w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">此外本次邀請到《別當歐尼醬了！》作者「貓豆腐」舉辦簽名活動，並推出可參與活動限量的iPASS簽名套組，每日限量20份。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"801\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010958/ff45dlsitefirstnews03.jpg\" alt=\"ff45dlsitefirstnews03\" class=\"wp-image-42779\" title=\"DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會 4\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010958/ff45dlsitefirstnews03.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010958/ff45dlsitefirstnews03-300x240.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02010958/ff45dlsitefirstnews03-768x615.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※簽名會套組售罄後，iPASS限定套組仍會販售，惟無參與活動資格。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※iPASS也提供非簽名套組版的單體販售。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"> FF45將於8月22日－8月24日，在圓山花博爭豔館舉辦，更多「DLsite」參展資訊將陸續更新。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"706\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02011003/ff45dlsitefirstnews04.jpg\" alt=\"ff45dlsitefirstnews04\" class=\"wp-image-42780\" title=\"DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會 5\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02011003/ff45dlsitefirstnews04.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02011003/ff45dlsitefirstnews04-300x212.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/02011003/ff45dlsitefirstnews04-768x542.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">「DLsite」官網</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42776\">DLsite公開首波FF45參展情報 將邀請《別當歐尼醬了！》作者貓豆腐來台舉辦簽名會</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "post-id": {
            "_attributes": {
              "xmlns": "com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"
            },
            "_text": "42776"
          }
