        {
          "title": {
            "_text": "hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台"
          },
          "link": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42754"
          },
          "dc:creator": {
            "_cdata": "萌朧雪猴"
          },
          "pubDate": {
            "_text": "Fri, 01 Aug 2025 11:52:23 +0000"
          },
          "category": [
            {
              "_cdata": "Vtuber"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "模型周邊"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "Hololive"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "和飲九九"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=42754"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>由SAKEBOYS企劃，東長酒造釀造，攜手hololive English旗下Vtuber「Ninomae Ina'nis(一伊那爾栖，一伊那尓栖）」，推出的限定聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」，日商和飲九九於8月1日宣布代理入台，調查表單開放中。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42754\">hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">由<a href=\"https://sakeboys.jp/en/collections/sakeboys/products/inatsu-junmaidaiginjo-goodsset\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://sakeboys.jp/en/collections/sakeboys/products/inatsu-junmaidaiginjo-goodsset\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SAKEBOYS</a>企劃，東長酒造釀造，攜手hololive English旗下Vtuber「Ninomae Ina&#8217;nis(一伊那爾栖，一伊那尓栖）」，推出的限定聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」，日商和飲九九於8月1日宣布代理入台，調查表單開放中。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"652\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194917/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01-1024x652.jpg\" alt=\"2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01\" class=\"wp-image-42755\" title=\"hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台 6\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194917/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01-1024x652.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194917/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01-300x191.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194917/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01-768x489.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194917/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」，呼應「一伊那爾栖」的紫色主色調，酒標則印有「一伊那爾栖」穿上浴衣的可愛姿態，在和飲九九的商品介紹頁提到，這款酒帶來輕盈的口感和淡淡的果香。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"918\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194921/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02-918x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02\" class=\"wp-image-42756\" title=\"hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台 7\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194921/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02-918x1024.jpg 918w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194921/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02-269x300.jpg 269w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194921/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02-768x857.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194921/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo02.jpg 1076w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 918px) 100vw, 918px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」同時也有清酒瓶、豬口杯、壓克力立牌的周邊套組，目前已在和飲九九線上商店限定開放預購，售價為1,780元。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"919\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194923/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03-919x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03\" class=\"wp-image-42757\" title=\"hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台 8\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194923/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03-919x1024.jpg 919w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194923/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03-269x300.jpg 269w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194923/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03-768x856.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194923/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo03.jpg 949w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 919px) 100vw, 919px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」的調查表單也已開放，根據表單說明頁面，將會提供&nbsp;720ml.的款式，售價則為3900元，預定10月抵達，並以冷運配送。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"656\" height=\"175\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194926/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo04.jpg\" alt=\"2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo04\" class=\"wp-image-42758\" title=\"hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台 9\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194926/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo04.jpg 656w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01194926/2025wain99twsakeboysinatsujunmaidaiginjo04-300x80.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※調查表單為不含周邊的單瓶款式</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">調查表單將開放至2025年8月6日，但超過調查數量亦有可能提前關閉調查表單，提交表單後，還需於期限內至經銷商完成預購，欲入手者須多加留意。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※禁止酒駕，飲酒過量有礙健康</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://wain99online.com/zh/products/%E4%BC%8A%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BE%A1%E7%8C%AA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A3%93%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E7%AB%8B%E7%89%8C%E7%B5%84\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://wain99online.com/zh/products/%E4%BC%8A%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BE%A1%E7%8C%AA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A3%93%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E7%AB%8B%E7%89%8C%E7%B5%84\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」周邊套組線上預購頁面 </a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNQeuKSwDlLjOVNqZZGB2aGAB-FjUKZBgRGJrStTGCARXrpQ/viewform\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfNQeuKSwDlLjOVNqZZGB2aGAB-FjUKZBgRGJrStTGCARXrpQ/viewform\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">調查表單頁面</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42754\">hololive「一伊那爾栖」聯名純米大吟釀「伊夏」確定由和飲九九代理入台</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
