          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>華人最大電玩動漫社群網站「巴哈姆特」，正式公開今年網站年度盛事「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」，將於2025年12月27日於台北花博爭艷館舉辦，「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿」同步開跑，入選創作者作品有機會成為場刊封面。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42738\">「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">華人最大電玩動漫社群網站「巴哈姆特」，正式公開今年網站年度盛事「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」，將於2025年12月27日於台北花博爭艷館舉辦，「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿」同步開跑，入選創作者作品有機會成為場刊封面。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01\" class=\"wp-image-42739\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 10\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-300x150.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-768x384.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">我們是從2022年的<a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/15673\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/15673\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">「巴哈姆特 26 週年站聚」</a>開始獲邀前往採訪，作為巴哈姆特的年度盛事，「巴哈姆特 26 週年站聚」當時是在台大體育館舉辦，雖然受限場地規模，但動漫電玩通大賽、電玩瘋大亂鬥、板主及玩家自行規劃的板攤區、販售二手與原創動漫周邊的市集區、在場外特設痛車展示區、入口處的賀圖聯展專區仍一樣不少。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191604/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews02.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews02\" class=\"wp-image-42740\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 11\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191604/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews02.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191604/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews02-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191604/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews02-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而「巴哈姆特 26 週年站聚」印象最深刻的大概是「灼眼的夏娜」版攤，不僅能再次看到傲嬌代表的青春回憶，還能看到各種珍貴逸品。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191608/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews04.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews04\" class=\"wp-image-42742\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 12\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191608/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews04.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191608/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews04-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191608/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews04-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">2023年的<a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/20579\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/20579\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">「巴哈姆特 27 週年站聚」</a>，則移師於圓山花博爭艷館舉辦，最大特色是首度以免費大辦桌形式舉辦，當然賀圖聯展、ACG 市集、痛車展也不缺席。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191610/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews05.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews05\" class=\"wp-image-42743\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 13\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191610/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews05.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191610/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews05-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191610/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews05-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">不過印象最深刻的當然還是，邀集到1200 名會員到場享用，結合遊戲、動漫畫族群熟悉的用語，如「從零開始的辦桌」、「為美好的辦桌獻上貓飯大集合」、「星爆氣流斬之見佛殺佛」等，由國宴級總鋪師水蛙師準備的餐點，可以說既好吃又有梗，連爆米花都能找到笑點。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191611/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews06.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews06\" class=\"wp-image-42744\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 14\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191611/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews06.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191611/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews06-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191611/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews06-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191613/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews07.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews07\" class=\"wp-image-42745\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 15\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191613/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews07.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191613/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews07-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191613/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews07-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">2024年的<a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/29935\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/29935\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">「巴哈姆特 28 週年站聚」</a>，同樣在圓山花博爭艷館舉辦，每年sega致詞都會提到的「站聚會下雨」，也已成為巴哈站聚的經典。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"771\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191615/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews08.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews08\" class=\"wp-image-42746\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 16\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191615/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews08.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191615/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews08-300x231.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191615/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews08-768x592.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">這屆站聚印象比較深刻的，大概就是電玩廠商更積極的投入宣傳，像Nintendo除了龐大攤位外 ，還設置了商品販售區。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191616/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews09.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews09\" class=\"wp-image-42747\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 17\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191616/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews09.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191616/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews09-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191616/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews09-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">另外當時站聚著重的採訪重點是「Vtuber」，現在回頭看報導，有些身影翩然離去，有些身影咬牙努力，加上一些無法明言的事，內心也是百感交集。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191620/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews11.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews11\" class=\"wp-image-42749\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 18\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191620/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews11.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191620/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews11-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191620/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews11-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191621/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews12.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews12\" class=\"wp-image-42750\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 19\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191621/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews12.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191621/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews12-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191621/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews12-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而針對「巴哈姆特站聚」，巴哈姆特每年都會先行徵稿，本次創作主題為「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日」，不論是熱鬧派對、奇幻慶典、學園活動或勇者與龍娘的舞台應援……只要能表達對巴哈姆特的生日祝福，風格不限，都可自由發揮。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01\" class=\"wp-image-42739\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 10\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-300x150.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01-768x384.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191603/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">今年巴哈生日賀圖活動也會在站聚設置「賀圖聯展專區」，並同步收錄於限量發行的「巴哈姆特 29 週年紀念場刊」中，展出後的原尺寸輸出畫作更將贈與創作者本人，過往的「賀圖聯展專區」可參考我們先前的現場實照。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191606/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews03.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews03\" class=\"wp-image-42741\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 21\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191606/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews03.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191606/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews03-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191606/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews03-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191618/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews10.jpg\" alt=\"2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews10\" class=\"wp-image-42748\" title=\"「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中 22\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191618/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews10.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191618/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews10-300x225.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/01191618/2025forumgamersiteeventpostnews10-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">此外，「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿」入選創作者不僅可獲得「29 週年限定紀念勳章」、10,000 巴幣獎勵，還有機會讓作品成為場刊封面，獲頒「紀念商品組」並留下永久紀錄，在這個許多事物已數位化的時代，還能有機會變成人手一本實體本的封面，確實是難能可貴的機會。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」，將於2025年12月27日於台北花博爭艷館舉辦，「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿」，從8月1日－ 10月31日，預計11月10日公布入選名單，11月24日－ 12月7日為人氣票選，並於12月10日公布得獎者名單，對徵稿與活動有興趣的人，可前往巴哈姆特<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60146&amp;snA=7334&amp;tnum=1&amp;subbsn=3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">哈啦區</a>，了解更多徵稿和站聚活動細節。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿企劃</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">&nbsp;活動時程</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">報名交件：8/1（五）～ 10/31（五）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">入選公布：11/10（一）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">人氣票選：11/24（一）～ 12/7（日）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">得獎公布：12/10（三）</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">獎項內容</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">入選獎：作品將於站聚當日展出，並獲得 10,000 巴幣與 29 週年限定紀念勳章</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">優勝獎：一件作品將成為紀念場刊「封面」，獲頒紀念商品組</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">人氣獎：開放玩家票選，得票最高者可獲得人氣獎紀念商品組（與優勝獎分開評選）</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">作品規格</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">A4 單張直式彩色作品（21×29.7cm，300dpi，CMYK）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">檔案格式為 TIFF 或高解析 JPEG</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">僅限本人原創作品，禁止使用 AI 或違反著作權之內容</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">請將所有文字轉為圖層後再存檔，鼓勵電繪與手繪皆參加</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">場刊收錄方式</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">優勝作品：場刊整頁呈現，並附創作者筆名與介紹</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">入選作品：盡量以整頁呈現，依實際排版狀況調整</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">投稿方式</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">於巴哈姆特網站【創作大廳】點選「我要投稿」，選擇「插畫&#8211;巴哈姆特 29 週年慶賀圖」類別。附上作者筆名與創作發想後，再於「繳交原稿」上傳原始檔（AI 或 PSD 檔）及 JPG 檔備存。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">巴哈姆特 29 週年站聚活動情報</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">日期：2025/12/27（六）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">時間：10:00～18:00</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">地點：花博爭豔館（台北市中山區玉門街 1 號）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">票價：免費入場</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.gamer.com.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.gamer.com.tw/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">巴哈姆特官網</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60146&amp;snA=7334&amp;tnum=1&amp;subbsn=3\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60146&amp;snA=7334&amp;tnum=1&amp;subbsn=3\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> 「巴哈姆特 29 歲生日賀圖徵稿」特設文章頁面</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42738\">「巴哈姆特29周年站聚」12月27日將於花博爭艷館舉辦 生日賀圖徵稿中</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
