          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>漢堡王攜手《火影忍者》的聯名活動現正進行中，除推出2款火影限定漢堡、火影忍者雙人餐、火影地瓜薯外，還有火影皇冠帽、火影模型等搭配特典。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42725\">漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">漢堡王攜手《火影忍者》的聯名活動現正進行中，除推出2款火影限定漢堡、火影忍者雙人餐、火影地瓜薯外，還有火影皇冠帽、火影模型等搭配特典。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233116/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto01.jpg\" alt=\"2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto01\" class=\"wp-image-42726\" title=\"漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品 23\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233116/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto01.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233116/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto01-300x127.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233116/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto01-768x324.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">漢堡王X火影忍者2款限定漢堡，有火影華堡及火影雞排堡。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233121/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto03.jpg\" alt=\"2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto03\" class=\"wp-image-42728\" title=\"漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品 24\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233121/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto03.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233121/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto03-300x169.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233121/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto03-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">火影華堡：5吋大漢堡＋火烤純牛肉＋日式照燒醬＋橘色系麵包</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">火影雞排堡：超大雞腿排＋多層次鮮蔬＋日式照燒醬＋橘色系麵包</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">火影地瓜薯則是用鳴人圖案的外盒放入金黃色的地瓜薯，我們自己還塞了根一般薯條當白頭髮。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1008\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233124/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04.jpg\" alt=\"2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04\" class=\"wp-image-42729\" title=\"漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品 25\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233124/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233124/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04-298x300.jpg 298w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233124/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04-150x150.jpg 150w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233124/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto04-768x774.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">而單點漢堡或A、B、C套餐（不含外送平台）就送火影皇冠帽，共5款隨機贈；臨櫃購買「火影華堡/雞排堡公仔套餐」，專屬贈品為鳴人、小櫻模型，不過各地店家陸續完售，但據說會有新一波的角色。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233119/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto02.jpg\" alt=\"2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto02\" class=\"wp-image-42727\" title=\"漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品 26\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233119/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto02.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233119/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto02-300x169.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/31233119/2025julyBurgerKingTWnaruto02-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">漢堡王X火影忍者活動進行中，更多資訊可留意漢堡王官網或社群專頁。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://burgerking.com.tw/category/1#105\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://burgerking.com.tw/category/1#105\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">漢堡王官網 </a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">漢堡</a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">王</a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingTW/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FB</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/42725\">漢堡王Ｘ火影忍者聯名活動 推出火影地瓜薯、火影華堡等主題餐點與贈品</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
